  "title": "Logistics Executive - F10",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>· Manage 3PL/warehouse partners; plan & track inbound/outbound shipments.</p><p>· Negotiate rates with couriers, forwarders & consolidators; maintain a freight quote database.</p><p>·Prepare weekly/monthly dashboards on cost, OTD, transit time & exceptions.</p><p>·Ensure accurate documentation, permits and compliance with trade regulations.</p><p>· Initiate SOP/CI improvements to reduce cost and cycle time.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>· 3 years’ logistics experience (3PL operations, freight, documentation).</p><p>·Proven rate negotiation skills and vendor performance management.</p><p>·Knowledge of Incoterms, HS codes and import/export permits.<br /></p><p><strong>WORKING AREA - ISLAND WIDE - (NOT WFH) </strong><br /></p><p>TALENT LINK SOLUTION – (23C1962)</p><p>PATRICK POH</p><p>Reg No - R1107847</p><p>WhatsApp- +659108969</p>",
